{"tid":1420487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊討論下「光復香港 時代革命」呢句口號","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:16:58.000Z","uid":73897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3993727b327b1e8d68bcef47c9e5ee1467d1e9","tid":1420487,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/507701875/posts/10156106250271876?s=1404998993&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F507701875%2Fposts%2F10156106250271876%3Fs%3D1404998993%26sfns%3Dmo&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnNjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=2e31eee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/507701875/posts/10156106250271876?s=1404998993&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n本民前賦予嘅意義：<br />\n前句代表佢地組織成立以嚟嘅行動<br />\n後句代表佢地嘅信念同定位<br />\n<br />\n記者會都有講到呢句口號嘅意義可能有新舊之別<br />\n<br />\n想睇下各位抗爭者會唔會有自己嘅見解可以分享下"},{"pid":"c84490a59c5e092d04cfc2bf890763f791014018","tid":1420487,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7254cefe4808239364aeb46193973ab2a5a876e3","tid":1420487,"uid":73897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:19:17.000Z","msg":"拋磚先<br />\n我覺得<br />\n光復香港：<br />\n就係為香港帶來昔日嘅平和景象，將侵略者徹底驅逐，守護我地自己嘅家園。侵略者不限於平日出賣我地以換取自身利益嘅組織／政府官員。<br />\n<br />\n時代革命：<br />\n我地追隨民主自由平等呢幾樣樣普世價值，同時追求真正嘅香港自治，我地會用唔同嘅方法去嘗試，直至我地嘅信念能夠實現。所以呢一次運動將會係我地身處嘅呢一個時代嘅一場變革，為香港帶來民主自由嘅一場革命。"},{"pid":"4cf4ccbf9215b417fdcc79e6b40899168b6e1ccd","tid":1420487,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"１０連推"},{"pid":"b559bcd1d0a8c17997fab641df4afcb13e3f94b0","tid":1420487,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"９"},{"pid":"c61ce7920fac37f1ecacf24b424f1c7e6d836895","tid":1420487,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"８"},{"pi